                        <figure class="mb-25"><img class="w-100 img-fluid rounded mb-3 shadow-sm" style="max-height: 480px; object-fit: cover;" src="/style/brand/img/cift-acilir-tente1.webp" alt="ift Alr Tente" loading="lazy" /></figure>
